INSERT INTO email_kb_index (message_id, slug, created_at, notion_page_id)
VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
ON CONFLICT (message_id) DO NOTHING;

Params:
$1 = ={{ $json.messageId }}
$2 = ={{ $json.slug }}
$3 = ={{ $json.sentAt }}
$4 = ={{ $node["Create a database page"].json.id }}
Replace with your actual Notion node name.

